    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Schur Q-Polynomials and Kontsevich-Witten Tau Function
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Liu%2C+X">Xiaobo Liu</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Yang%2C+C">Chenglang Yang</a>
      
    </p>
    
    <p class="abstract mathjax">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Abstract</span>:
      <span class="abstract-short has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.14318v1-abstract-short" style="display: inline;">
        In this paper, we prove a conjecture of Mironov and Morozov which expresses Kontsevich-Witten tau-function as a linear combination of Schur Q-polynomials. We also prove Alexandrov&#39;s conjecture that Kontsevich-Witten tau-function is a hypergeometric tau-function of the BKP hierarchy after re-scaling.
        
      </span>
      <span class="abstract-full has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.14318v1-abstract-full" style="display: none;">
        In this paper, we prove a conjecture of Mironov and Morozov which expresses Kontsevich-Witten tau-function as a linear combination of Schur Q-polynomials. We also prove Alexandrov&#39;s conjecture that Kontsevich-Witten tau-function is a hypergeometric tau-function of the BKP hierarchy after re-scaling.
        <a class="is-size-7" style="white-space: nowrap;" onclick="document.getElementById('2103.14318v1-abstract-full').style.display = 'none'; document.getElementById('2103.14318v1-abstract-short').style.display = 'inline';">&#9651; Less</a>
