    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Classical $n$-body scattering with long-range potentials
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=F%C3%A9joz%2C+J">Jacques Féjoz</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Knauf%2C+A">Andreas Knauf</a>, 
      
