        A semi-theoretical method to detect classical monodromy
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Omiste%2C+J+J">Juan J. Omiste</a>, 
      
