        <span>&nbsp;[<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2103.12929">pdf</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/ps/2103.12929">ps</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/format/2103.12929">other</a>]&nbsp;</span>
