    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Multicomponent coagulation systems: existence and non-existence of stationary non-equilibrium solutions
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Ferreira%2C+M+A">Marina A. Ferreira</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Lukkarinen%2C+J">Jani Lukkarinen</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Nota%2C+A">Alessia Nota</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Vel%C3%A1zquez%2C+J+J+L">Juan J. L. Velázquez</a>
      
