        Mirror symmetry for extended affine Weyl groups
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Brini%2C+A">Andrea Brini</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=van+Gemst%2C+K">Karoline van Gemst</a>
      
