    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Variance of voltages in a lattice Coulomb gas
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Conache%2C+D">Diana Conache</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Heydenreich%2C+M">Markus Heydenreich</a>, 
      
