    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Stabilization and blow-up in the relativistic model of cold collisional plasma
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Rozanova%2C+O+S">Olga S. Rozanova</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Chizhonkov%2C+E+V">Eugeniy V. Chizhonkov</a>
      
