    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        $\mathbb{Z}_2^3$-Graded extensions of Lie superalgebras and superconformal quantum mechanics
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Doi%2C+S">S. Doi</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Aizawa%2C+N">N. Aizawa</a>
      
