    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Bootstrapping the half-BPS line defect CFT in $\mathcal{N}=4$ SYM at strong coupling
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Ferrero%2C+P">Pietro Ferrero</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Meneghelli%2C+C">Carlo Meneghelli</a>
      
